                "respRate": [
                    {
                        "lang": "fr",
                        "value": "27 000 personnes r\u00e9pondant au questionnaire d'inclusion en 2017-2018 constituant la cohorte active ; 90 000 personnes dans la cohorte passive (27 000 r\u00e9pondants + environ 63 000 individus non r\u00e9pondants au questionnaire) : recueil SNDS, donn\u00e9es administratives des R\u00e9gimes et CNAV"
                    },
                    {
                        "lang": "en",
                        "value": "30,000 for nationwide study; 60,000 individuals that did not respond to the questionnaire were passively monitored (BMA); 2,500 active workers from the agricultural scheme in the pilot cohort;+7,500 non-respondents to the questionnaire passively monitored. Extended: 30,000 active agricultural workers in the cohort + sample of 60,000 non-respondents to the questionnaire."
                    }
                ]
            }
