            "qualityStatement": {
                "standardsCompliance": {},
                "otherQualityStatement": [
                    {
                        "lang": "fr",
                        "value": "Contr\u00f4le coh\u00e9rence au moment de la saisie des donn\u00e9es informatiques Gestion de la non-r\u00e9ponse partielle ou de vague par imputation et correction de la non-r\u00e9ponse totale par re-pond\u00e9ration gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 l'exploitation de donn\u00e9es externes (bases assurances maladie et vieillesse) collect\u00e9es pour r\u00e9pondants et \u00e9chantillon de non r\u00e9pondants Les patients sont inform\u00e9s de l'utilisation de leur donn\u00e9es par \u00e9crit au moment de l'inclusion"
                    },
                    {
                        "lang": "en",
                        "value": "Consistency checks during computerised data entry. Management of partial or wave non-response by imputation and correction of complete non-response through re-weighting using leveraged external data (health insurance and pension databases) collected for respondents and non-respondent sample. Individuals are informed about the use of their data in writing at baseline."
                    }
                ]
            },
